    <svcproc svcproctype="clean" graphiccount="0">
        <title>Clean Axle Assemblies</title>
        <randlist type="bullet">
            <item>
                <para>A completely assembled axle assembly can be steam cleaned on the outside to remove heavy amounts
                    of dirt.
                </para>
            </item>
            <item>
                <para>Before the axle is steam cleaned, close or put a cover over all openings in the axle assembly.
                    Examples of openings are breathers or vents in air chambers.
                </para>
            </item>
        </randlist>
    </svcproc>
